One of the most special Sunday’s I’ve ever had 🙏🏼 My friend Charlie Parker ( @acenetting ) asked me to baptize him! I was honored and blessed to do so! This was a special and difficult moment as Charlie has been battling liver cancer for a year and a half. The doctors gave him a couple months to live 2 weeks ago. Praying for a miracle 🙏🏼 Charlie’s faith over the last couple years has been nothing short of inspiring! Thank you Charlie for your witness and standing on your faith in Jesus through it all🙏🏼🙌🏼

Picacho Baptist Church service 4/30/23
@abbisheneman

2023 American Grand Prix Fitasc Championship was awesome! Some great Fitasc targets set. I was blessed to have won HOA after a shoot off with fellow World Champ @greggwolfgotinsta 🙏🏼 @karenkmiles finished 3rd overall after a shoot off with @andrewwysocky ! Very proud of my wife. @fennellshootingschool continues to dominate the Veteran category.

Karen and I are extremely proud of a couple students who medaled in Super Vet! My student Paul Oppegaurd won gold and our student @rstrudeau was silver! 

Congrats to @zkienbaum on winning the Trident Cup HOA over Karen. Congrats to all the winners. 

Thanks to @meadowsclaysports @dombethel for an awesome job on Fitasc 🙏🏼

social_posts.post_text: Absolutely stunning landscape to shoot targets on! @littletrapperinc had one of the most spectacular venues for @karenkmiles @clay_shooting_joe and me to practice on last week. What a blessing to get to practice and coach on some incredible terrain! Off to UK today 🙏🏼🙌🏼
They stole almost everything (passports, cash, gun permits, etc..)￼, except for our guns and dirty clothes ￼in London today, lol.

New passports, gun permits and Pilla glasses from @claytargetvision in 40hrs 🙏🏼🙌🏼 Wow God is a provider! Thank you to everyone who prayed and provided help!
Kate Digweed helped us with getting ready for the US Embassy 🙏🏼
@cpsauk @iain_cpsa @ejchurchill , @robfenwick1 and staff helping us get gun permits first thing Tuesday morning 🙏🏼
Nigel Bough gave us some funds 🙏🏼
Dennis Sprenger is just incredible! They made new glasses for me within an hour after I contacted him and had them to the UK in 36 hours￼! Just wow! 
May you all be blessed 10 fold for blessing us!

When I got my shooting gear stolen in London, @densprenger of @claytargetvision made some new prescription @pillaperformanceeyewear glasses for me and had them to me in a few days. @castellani_usa contacted @castellani_official and had a new vest for me by Hungary. 

The companies that support me are incredible and I’m extremely blessed to be part of Pilla, Castellani, @krieghoff_international @baschieri_pellagriusa @baschieriepellagri @laporte_clay_shooting @mullerchokescompetition @soundgear_official
Join us tomorrow at Western Regional 🙏🏼🤍

Happy birthday to my dad! @timothygmiles I love you so much!

I accepted Jesus into my heart as my Lord and Savior! I hope that I can use the talents he gave me to share his word! @barepelt @barepeltfamilyphotography @fabarmusa @gameboreus @juniorshootersmagazine @mecoutdoors.official @soundgear_official @pillaperformanceeyewear @scorechaser @willienation1 #jesuschrist #shotgun #sportingclays @mysctp

Had fun at the South Central Regional at @coveyriselodge ! Congrats to @_toddhitch on a dominant performance and winning HOA. Happy for @shelby_n_moon27 for winning her first regional, and thankful for her wedding gift (last slide) 🙏🏼 I’m proud of my wife for  battling back after a rough start to the week and winning the @winchesterammunition lady’s cup 💪🏼💪🏼 I managed RU what n Fitasc to @kevindemichiel and won a sweet @maruccisports bat 💪🏼💪🏼😅 Good targets all week.

So happy for my friend @rstrudeau on his hard work and finishing RU at another fitasc team qualifier! On his way to reaching a goal 💪🏼💪🏼

2023 Nationals in the books! We enjoyed our time competing in the @nationalsportingclaysassoc Super Squad. Congrats to @brandon_powell_sporting.clays on winning his first National Championship. I’m proud of my former student, Bayne Horne (the tall man in the second video) on his runner up. Congrats to @mvsharpe2001 on winning the ladies main event. Congrats to all the winners and everyone who shot well.

I’m proud of my wife @karenkmiles for battling all week without having her A game to finish RU in ladies and win the season long @winchesterammunition Ladies Cup for the third year in a row. But, I’m more proud of the way that she lives out the gospel and is not afraid to make Jesus name known and show His love! 

The Nationals concludes our shooting season and we could not do this without our sponsors!

@brandon_powell_sporting.clays texted me right before we started our final round of Nationals on Sunday. Our 2023 National Champion is humble enough and bold enough to worship Jesus in the midst of the highest level of competition. He’s grown a ton over the years. Our God is a God of forgiveness and redemption. Maybe we should be too 🙏🏼🤍

We stopped by @pineridgefarmtn to check out what @jwright37043 , @melissa_always_wright and my dad @timothygmiles are working on in TN. We may be in the area a little bit next year since @abbisheneman & @jeremiahsheneman just moved to the Franklin area.

@karenkmiles and I have been working w/ @susiemeyersgolf and we love learning from her. She has helped us swing effortlessly. She was showing me an impact feel that I needed from @tigerwoods . I saw a video recently by @golfslump who showed @granthorvat talking about that same feel that he saw from Tiger! That feel helped me not only hit it longer than I ever have but also more consistently straight today! 18 out of 20 drivers on the range landed w/in a 20 yard radius between 305-330. I normally carry the ball 285-305
#golf
